text: We just received this resume from an agency.   I had just heard this morning
that an economist was coming into your group, so I don't know if you are
interested or not.    Let me know if I can be of any help.

blocks.subject: Resume for Vince Kaminski
text: Johnathan is at 142,000 base + 10-15% bonus. He is a PhD., Certified in
Financial Risk Management, awaiting Charter as CFA, and the list goes
on. At KPMG his clients are Financial Institutions, e-commerce, internet,
and high tech. He has real options valuation and various other financial
and overall corporate risk valuation and analysis skills that may be of
interest to Vince and his group.
